data.title: Brand New Apartments in Woodburn Oregon
data.meta_description: BRAND NEW modern apartments in Woodburn, Oregon. Discover our beautiful interiors with 1, 2, or 3 bedrooms and community amenities you'll love!
data.text:
Welcome to Woodburn Villas, where you'll find the perfect blend of modern luxury and natural beauty. Our stunningly beautiful setting offers an abundance of comfort, with spacious apartments that boast upgraded finishes and amenities. You'll enjoy the convenience of air conditioning, quartz counters, and stainless steel appliances, all designed to make your life easier and more enjoyable.

Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a place to entertain, Woodburn Villas has everything you need to live your best life. Come see for yourself why our community is the perfect place to call home!

Our community offers a variety of floor plans to suit your needs, with 1, 2, or 3 bedroom options available. At Woodburn Villas, we believe that life should be both comfortable and fun, which is why we offer a wide range of amenities that will make you feel right at home. Relax with friends and family in our clubhouse, take a dip in our pool, or let the kids run wild in our splash pad. Stay active with our fitness center and sports courts, or simply take a stroll through our beautifully landscaped grounds.

Explore photos of our outstanding community and see why people love calling Woodburn Villas home.
